far the quickest and easiest site I've ever made. Highly recommended!"},{author:"Monique Toms",body:"It is the easiest app that I have found for setting up and hosting a website, I have many years of experience with computers and searching the web but minimal in programming"},{author:"Bom Dia Network",body:"Has an inviting simplicity to create a website. You can't do anything wrong, everything happens so quickly that you just focus on the content."},{author:"Roger Holloway",body:"I was surprised how easy and intuitive the interface was, and had a bunch of fun creating my first website for real estate here in the Charlotte market."},{author:"WAN5 Geological Surveying Services",body:"Solo AI is great! It makes my website so easy, fast, simple, and less worrisome. My friends told me it was awesome and I am happy and grateful about it."},{author:"Jump & Shout Wellness Studios",body:"Solo is easy to use and comes with resources that provide answers to many questions. The staff is stellar and quick to respond to questions and inquiries. A great value that stands tall against competitors."}]},faqArea:{title:"Frequently asked questions",subtitle:"You can learn more in",soloSupport:"Solo Support",description:"Text here for SEO optimization",items:[{question:"What does Solo cost?",answer:"Solo AI website creator allows you to connect and host your custom domain for free. We are not going to put ads on your website. We also offer a <a href='https://soloist.ai/pricing'>Pro plan</a> for more features and websites."},{question:"Can I connect a custom domain to my Solo website?",answer:"After you set up your Solo website, you can connect a custom domain that is personalized to your business. Websites with custom domains see more traffic and as a result more business!"},{question:"Can I connect my scheduling service to my Solo site?",answer:"Yes, in the Scheduling section for your website, provide a link to your scheduling service whether Calendly, Tidycal or other."},{question:"Can I link to my existing social media pages?",answer:"Yes, you can provide links to all of your social presences and display them in the Header and Footer of your website."},{question:"Can I sell products on my website?",answer:"Yes. You can use the Services section type to add your products and services pricing and use payment links from Stripe or Paypal linked in the button so your users can complete the payment. Note: You have to fulfill the product or service yourself directly to the user."},{question:"Can I invite editors to my website?",answer:"Yes. You can use the Invite Editor feature that you can access from the Share button in the top toolbar and invite a user to edit the website or transfer ownership to them."},{question:"How can I add a chatbot to my website?",answer:"You can use the Custom Code option available in Settings to insert the chatbot embed code based on the chatbot provider you have chosen."},{question:"Is my website mobile-friendly?",answer:"Yes. Solo AI Website Creator optimizes your website for desktop and mobile from the start so it looks great on any device, with no extra work required from you."},{question:"How can I edit or update the content on my Solo website?",answer:"You can visit <a href='https://soloist.ai/designer'>https://soloist.ai/designer</a>, login to your account using the method you used to sign up (Google or Email), and start making the changes as needed."},{question:"Does Solo offer discounts to nonprofits?",answer:"Yes. Solo AI website creator offers a discount to eligible nonprofits. Please <a href='mailto:support@soloist.ai'>contact us</a> to learn more."}]},callToActionArea:{title:"Ready to start creating?",description:"Get your free website in just minutes after answering a few short questions",button:"Create Your Website",buttonLabel:"Solo AI Onboarding Page (opens in a new tab)"},title:"Solo - Free AI Website Creator",siteName:"Solo - Free AI Website Creator",siteDescription:"Create a beautiful website for your bu